title: Google\Cloud\Dlp\V2\InfoType
name: InfoType
description:
Type of information detected by the API.

Generated from protobuf message google.privacy.dlp.v2.InfoType

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: Name of the information type. Either a name of your choosing when creating a CustomInfoType, or one of the names listed at https://cloud.google.com/dlp/docs/infotypes-reference when specifying a built-in type. When sending Cloud DLP results to Data Catalog, infoType names should conform to the pattern [A-Za-z0-9$-_]{1,64}.
